room_title: Escape room "Uncle Tick Tock's Circus" by Escape Room Napa in Rohnert Park
room_description: Come one, come all! Witness the marvel and the mystery of the circus world. Clowns, Acrobats, Circus Animals and more await you. Can you solve the mystery and win the ultimate prize? Are you of keen mind and spirit to evade the pitfalls of circus life? Will you be a puppet or the puppet master? Will your team make it in time? This will be a topsy-turvy adventure that will keep you on the high wire of life. Life is a Circus, Will you enjoy the show? And remember, it takes a Clown to beat the Circus.
